OL,3,CPolice release CCTV images of three
OL,4,Cmen following assault
OL,6,FPolice have released CCTV images of
OL,7,Fthree men they would like to speak
OL,8,Fwith in relation with a serious
OL,9,Fassault in Maidstone.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to an incident on
OL,12,Fthe high street between the junctions
OL,13,Fwith Mill Street and Fairmeadow just
OL,14,Fafter 4:30am on Sunday 28 June.
OL,16,FA man in his 30s was treated for stab
OL,17,Fwounds. He was taken to a London
OL,18,Fhospital where his condition is
OL,19,Fdescribed as serious but stable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
