OL,3,CPolice release CCTV images of three
OL,4,Cmen following assault
OL,6,FA second man in his 20s, who had a cut
OL,7,Fto his arm, was treated at a local
OL,8,Fhospital.
OL,10,FIt is alleged the two victims were
OL,11,Finjured during an altercation with a
OL,12,Fgroup of people.
OL,14,FKent Police has released the CCTV
OL,15,Fimages as part of its investigation
OL,16,Finto the circumstances surrounding the
OL,17,Fincident. It's thought the men might
OL,18,Fbe able to assist officers with their
OL,19,Fenquiries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
