OL,3,CPolice release CCTV images of three
OL,4,Cmen following assault
OL,6,FAnyone who might have witnessed what
OL,7,Fhappened, or residents or business
OL,8,Fowners with private CCTV, are also
OL,9,Fbeing asked to contact the police on
OL,10,F01622 604100, quoting reference 46/
OL,11,F103621/26.
